---
import { Image } from "astro:assets"
import troySpeaking from "@/assets/images/troy-speaking.jpg"
---

<section class="py-24 text-[#1A30FF]">
	<div class="max-w-[1480px] mx-auto px-24">
		<div class="mb-10 text-right flex flex-col items-end">
			<h2
				class="text-5xl font-condensed font-bold tracking-[-0.04em] mb-4 max-w-prose">
				How I can help you
			</h2>
			<p class="prose text-right text-[#1A30FF]">
				We're experts at what we do, but it didn't happen overnight. We've
				learned a lot over the years and we want to share that knowledge with
				you.
			</p>
		</div>
		<div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-20">
			<div class="order-2 relative aspect-square">
				<Image
					class="absolute w-full h-full object-cover"
					src={troySpeaking}
					alt="Troy speaking at a conference in Singapore"
				/>
				<div class="bg-[#1a31ff90] absolute w-full h-full top-2 left-2 -z-[1]">
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="space-y-8">
				<div class="prose text-[#1A30FF]">
					<div class="font-bold">Courses &amp; Training</div> We create courses on
					a variety of development topics, including guided training to skill up
					your team.
				</div>
				<hr class="prose text-[#1a31ff90]" />
				<div class="prose text-[#1A30FF]">
					<div class="font-bold">Freelance or Team Augmentation</div>
					I specialize in jumping into projects with tight deadlines that need a
					spark. If you or your team need something built fast and well, get in touch.
				</div>
				<hr class="prose text-[#1a31ff90]" />
				<div class="prose text-[#1A30FF]">
					<div class="font-bold">Code Reviews</div> Sometimes you need another set
					of ðŸ‘€ to review your code and provide valuable feedback. Our experienced
					team can help you improve the quality of your code and ensure best practices
					are followed.
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>
